wikipedia_page.main: Hannah Beard (born 22 August 1988) is an English association football player, who last played for Western Sydney Wanderers in the Australian W-League.As a youngster Beard turned out for FA Women's Premier League outfit Liverpool Ladies.Beard was one of two foreign players on Wanderers in 2014.In 2020, Beard played for the North Shore Mariners.
